<h2>Examples</h2>
<p>
  Avian is well-suited to building small, self-contained applications.
  To demonstrate this, we've taken a few demo applications from the
  Eclipse CVS repository and built them using
  Avian, <a href="http://proguard.sourceforge.net/">ProGuard</a>,
  and <a href="http://upx.sourceforge.net">UPX</a>.
</p>
